---
import Container from "./Container.astro";
---

<section id="pain-points" class="relative py-16 sm:py-24">
  <Container>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-12 lg:gap-16">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-mono font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-tight">
          Overprovisioned Resources
        </h3>
        <p class="text-ksctl-text-secondary leading-relaxed font-mono text-sm sm:text-base">
          You're paying for idle CPU and memory every month. Most teams overprovision by 40-60% and have no visibility into the waste.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-mono font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-tight">
          Blind to Energy Costs
        </h3>
        <p class="text-ksctl-text-secondary leading-relaxed font-mono text-sm sm:text-base">
          Without real energy data from your workloads, sustainability reporting is guesswork. Compliance deadlines don't wait for guesses.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-mono font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-tight">
          Efficiency Regressions Hide in Deploys
        </h3>
        <p class="text-ksctl-text-secondary leading-relaxed font-mono text-sm sm:text-base">
          You ship code, resource consumption creeps up, nobody notices until the bill arrives. Traditional monitoring doesn't track efficiency over time.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
